<p style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding:0px;"><b style="margin:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:楷体_GB2312;color:#000000;font-size:12pt;">客主商定租用房间价格包含（先付费用后使用）：</span></b></p>
<p></p>
<p style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:98pt;padding:0px;color:#d99694;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei';font-size:14px;line-height:22px;text-indent:-21pt;"><b style="margin:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:楷体_GB2312;color:#000000;font-size:12pt;">a<span style="font-family:宋体;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:楷体_GB2312;">水，电，气，网，停车及LAX接机一次。</span></span></b></p>
<p style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:98pt;padding:0px;color:#d99694;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei';font-size:14px;line-height:22px;text-indent:-21pt;"><b style="margin:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:楷体_GB2312;color:#000000;font-size:12pt;">b<span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:楷体_GB2312;">中美电话，</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:楷体_GB2312;color:#000000;font-size:12pt;">床上用品，厨房用品及中央空调，洗衣。</span></b></p>
<p style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:98pt;padding:0px;color:#d99694;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei';font-size:14px;line-height:22px;text-indent:-21pt;"><b style="margin:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:楷体_GB2312;color:#000000;font-size:12pt;">c<span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:楷体_GB2312;color:#000000;font-size:12pt;">待产每月4次医生产检直到BABY出生那天的接送。</span><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:楷体_GB2312;color:#000000;font-size:12pt;"><br />
</span><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:楷体_GB2312;color:#000000;font-size:12pt;">每周一次到COSTCO/TARGET/WAL-MART/BABYRUS采购。</span></b></p>
<p style="margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;margin-left:36pt;padding:0px;color:#d99694;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei';font-size:14px;line-height:22px;text-indent:-36pt;"><b style="margin:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:楷体_GB2312;color:#000000;font-size:12pt;">1，&nbsp;</span><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:楷体_GB2312;color:#000000;font-size:12pt;">待产报价，是按一个孕妇和另一个陪护人员（朋友，保姆，月嫂，婴儿都算是陪护人员），入住合约时间是以待产2个月，坐月子1个月为基准的;不含包餐(客人自煮)，不含个人购物接送（含集体采购/周）。如有需要包餐，另外面议。客人因特殊原因未到合约时间，提前离开（需15天前通知房东）的接机等费用需另外计算或商议。</span><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:楷体_GB2312;color:#000000;font-size:12pt;"><br />
</span><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:楷体_GB2312;color:#000000;font-size:12pt;">如果增加人数，按每增加一人每天USD10；&nbsp;</span></b></p>
<p style="margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;margin-left:36pt;padding:0px;color:#d99694;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei';font-size:14px;line-height:22px;text-indent:-36pt;"><b style="margin:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:楷体_GB2312;color:#000000;font-size:12pt;">2，&nbsp;</span><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:楷体_GB2312;color:#000000;font-size:12pt;">坐月子时因消耗水电气等各种成本及保险责任增加，每房每月（不按天计）需要增加USD300。</span></b></p>
<p style="margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;margin-left:36pt;padding:0px;color:#d99694;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei';font-size:14px;line-height:22px;text-indent:-36pt;"><b style="margin:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:楷体_GB2312;color:#000000;font-size:12pt;">3，&nbsp;</span><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:楷体_GB2312;color:#000000;font-size:12pt;">押金：客人离开前交还钥匙，并检查无物件损坏（如损坏请修复或更新好，注美国修复时工费高。）当时退还客人。</span></b></p>
<p style="margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;margin-left:17.7pt;padding:0px;color:#d99694;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei';font-size:14px;line-height:22px;text-indent:-17.64pt;"><b style="margin:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:楷体_GB2312;color:#000000;font-size:12pt;">4，医院产检接送：包括每月在周边附近区域（开车10分钟内）送产检4次，生产前及婴儿出院即止。孕妇家属的非产检及其它如需要用到车则另付费用，周边区域（3MILES以内）来回收USD20，3-5M收USD25稍远区域（5-8M）收30，到DOWNTOWN&nbsp;（12M）来回收40，到机场接机（28M）收50，送飞机场40。以上接送是指等待一小时以内的，&nbsp;如超过一小时一般按10美元/小时计，可议。</span><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:楷体_GB2312;color:#000000;font-size:12pt;">&nbsp;<span style="font-family:楷体_GB2312;">如客人后面租车没有费用退还。所有的接送以孕妇和婴儿为主，如果车空家人可以陪同（购物同效）。如要提供陪产价格面议。</span></span></b></p>
<p style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:17.7pt;padding:0px;color:#d99694;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei';font-size:14px;line-height:22px;text-indent:-17.64pt;"><b style="margin:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:楷体_GB2312;color:#000000;font-size:12pt;">5，房价中不包含（需要付费）内容：单独的超市购物和远区购物，餐饮，个人办证件，陪产，个人照料，办事旅游，延期，咨询，小孩上学，去打疫苗，回国停车等。</span></b></p>
<p style="margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;margin-left:17.7pt;padding:0px;color:#d99694;font-family:Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei';font-size:14px;line-height:22px;text-indent:-17.64pt;"><b style="margin:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:楷体_GB2312;color:#000000;font-size:12pt;">6，办理各种证件：代办费USD220，政府规定的费用客人自付。如果三个人以上团办可优惠，可议。&nbsp;</span></b></p>
