<p style="margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:medium;font-family:宋体;background-color:#eeece1;text-indent:153.15pt;line-height:16pt;"><b><span style="font-size:18pt;font-family:华文楷体;">安心服务项目<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>
<p style="margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:medium;font-family:宋体;background-color:#eeece1;text-indent:126.15pt;line-height:16pt;"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:18pt;font-family:华文楷体;">&nbsp;</span></b></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="margin:0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 36pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;background-color:#eeece1;text-indent:-36pt;line-height:16pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12pt;font-family:华文楷体;">1．<span style="font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:华文楷体;">多年月子中心工作经验厨师<span lang="EN-US">(</span>各地厨师，多种口味<span lang="EN-US">)</span>，精心烹饪精美膳食及炖<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="margin:0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 6pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;background-color:#eeece1;text-indent:6pt;line-height:16pt;"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:华文楷体;">补、精通各式月子调理；</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:华文楷体;">帮助您恢复身材及体质。</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:华文楷体;">牛奶、饮料、水果、点心无限量供应。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="margin:0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 36pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;background-color:#eeece1;line-height:16pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12pt;font-family:华文楷体;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="margin:0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 12pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;background-color:#eeece1;text-indent:-12pt;line-height:16pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12pt;font-family:华文楷体;">2.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:华文楷体;">专业护理<span lang="EN-US">24</span>小时照看婴儿，专业照顾，用心呵护。最多一对三服务，也可提供一对一服务您和您的宝宝。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12pt;font-family:华文楷体;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="margin-right:0cm;margin-left:18pt;font-size:medium;font-family:宋体;background-color:#eeece1;text-indent:-18pt;line-height:16pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:华文楷体;">3.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:华文楷体;">每周<span lang="EN-US">3</span>次购物休闲逛街及旅游安排，含高档精品购物中心及景区（统一安排，统一接送；详见《安心出行表》）；不定期安排</span><span style="font-family:华文楷体;">美国景点深度游<span lang="EN-US">(</span>自费<span lang="EN-US">)&nbsp;</span>。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:华文楷体;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="margin-right:0cm;margin-left:18pt;font-size:medium;font-family:宋体;background-color:#eeece1;text-indent:-18pt;line-height:16pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:华文楷体;">4</span><span style="font-family:华文楷体;">．免费语言学习课程安排<span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;(</span>需开课日<span lang="EN-US">)</span>。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:华文楷体;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
