<p style="margin-right:0cm;margin-left:18pt;font-size:medium;font-family:宋体;background-color:#eeece1;text-indent:-18pt;line-height:16pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:华文楷体;">6.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:华文楷体;">提供</span><span style="font-family:华文楷体;">电视、冰箱、空调、洗衣机、烘干机、微波炉、大床、床头柜、桌椅；厨具、餐具齐全；提供床上用品、浴巾、毛巾、洗发水、淋浴露、漱口杯、牙刷；无线高速宽带、免费国际长途电话（美、加、中港台）。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-right:0cm;margin-left:18pt;font-size:medium;font-family:宋体;background-color:#eeece1;text-indent:-18pt;line-height:16pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:华文楷体;">7.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:华文楷体;">提供代办宝宝证件服务；宝宝拍照服务。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
