>2005</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-hansi-font-family:'Times New Roman';">年，罗纳德</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">•</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-hansi-font-family:'Times New Roman';">里根医学中心被美国护理认证中心认证为具有最佳护理</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"> </span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-hansi-font-family:'Times New Roman';">品质的</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">“Magnet</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-hansi-font-family:'Times New Roman';">医院</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">”</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-hansi-font-family:'Times New Roman';">。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
