Stafford Leak Warren&nbsp;(1896.06.19 - 1981.07.26) </span></span><span style="font-size:small;"><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-hansi-font-family:'Times New Roman';">核医学家，加州大学旧金山分校医学院毕业，曾任</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Rochester</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-hansi-font-family:'Times New Roman';">大学原子能计划主任和</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">“</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-hansi-font-family:'Times New Roman';">曼哈顿计划</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">”</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-hansi-font-family:'Times New Roman';">医学部主任。</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">1947</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-hansi-font-family:'Times New Roman';">年参与创建</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">UCLA</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-hansi-font-family:'Times New Roman';">医学院，担任首任院长（</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">1947-1962</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-hansi-font-family:'Times New Roman';">）及核医学和放射生物学实验室主任（</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">1947-1955</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-hansi-font-family:'Times New Roman';">）。</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">1971</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-hansi-font-family:'Times New Roman';">年荣获美国政府颁发的费米奖。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-size:small;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-size:small;font-family:'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;<br />
William Polk Longmire Jr.&nbsp;(1913.09.14 - 2003.05.09) </span></span><span style="font-size:small;"><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-hansi-font-family:'Times New Roman';">外科学家。约翰</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">•</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-hansi-font-family:'Times New Roman';">霍普金斯大学医学院毕业，曾参与世界首例先天性心脏病婴儿手术（</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">1944</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-hansi-font-family:'Times New Roman';">年），后成为约翰</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">•</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-hansi-font-family:'Times New Roman';">霍普金斯医院整形外科主任。</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">1948</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-hansi-font-family:'Times New Roman';">年起担任</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">UCLA</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-hansi-font-family:'Times New Roman';">医学院首任外科主任（</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">1948-1976</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-hansi-font-family:'Times New Roman';">）。首创了胆道外科中的</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Longmire</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-hansi-font-family:'Times New Roman';">手术。曾任美国外科医师学院主席、美国外科理事会主席、爱丁堡和英格兰皇家外科医师学院荣誉会员。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
