<br style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;" />
<div align="left" style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;border:0px;padding:0px;">以前没弄过，所以详细的细则基本上是参考大家的细则写的<img src="http://www.bingege.org/static/image/smiley/default/handshake.gif" smilieid="23" border="0" alt="" style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;border:0px;padding:0px;vertical-align:middle;color:#555555;" />，如有不清楚和没说明的地方，本着人在异乡,相互体谅的原则，协商处理。</div>
<br style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;" />
<div align="left" style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;border:0px;padding:0px;">家里共4个房间。二楼套房<span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:'Times New Roman';">1</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:宋体;">间，有独立卫生间，二楼</span>雅房2<span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:宋体;">间，共用</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:'Times New Roman';">1</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:宋体;">个卫生间，一楼雅房</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:'Times New Roman';">1</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:宋体;">间，独立使用</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:'Times New Roman';">1</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:宋体;">个卫生间（卫生间门和房门挨着，基本上和套房差不多）。</span></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;border:0px;padding:0px;">关于租金：</div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;border:0px;padding:0px;">一楼雅房&nbsp;<span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:'Times New Roman';">1000</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:宋体;">刀</span>/月（独立使用<span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:'Times New Roman';">1</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:宋体;">个卫生间）</span></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;border:0px;padding:0px;">二楼套房&nbsp;<span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:'Times New Roman';">1200</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:宋体;">刀</span>/月</div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;border:0px;padding:0px;">二楼雅房&nbsp;&nbsp;900<span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:宋体;">刀</span>/月</div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;border:0px;padding:0px;">提示</div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;border:0px;padding:0px;">1、 以上价格为预订<span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:'Times New Roman';">3</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:宋体;">个月以上的的价格，不足月的部分，按照</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:'Times New Roman';">30</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:宋体;">天的百分比计算</span>；</div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;border:0px;padding:0px;">2、 陪客每人每天收<span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:'Times New Roman';">10</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:宋体;">刀，</span>7<span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:宋体;">岁以下孩子免费。</span></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;border:0px;padding:0px;">3、 预约试住、短住和入住不满一个月退房的按家庭旅馆收费，雅房每日50<span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:宋体;">刀</span>，套房每日<span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:'Times New Roman';">60</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:宋体;">刀。从决定长住开始，转长住另算</span>。</div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;border:0px;padding:0px;">4、 按月付月租，押金为500<span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:宋体;">刀</span>，提前两周通知离开，押金可退，未提前通知离开，押金不退；入住时一次性缴纳<span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:'Times New Roman';">3</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:宋体;">个月房租，免押金</span>，超过<span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:'Times New Roman';">3</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:宋体;">个月续交</span>。</div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;border:0px;padding:0px;">5、 做月子那个月加<span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:'Times New Roman';">200</span>刀，主要是水电煤气会高一些。</div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;border:0px;padding:0px;">6、 生产日期无法预测，早产或晚产结账时多退少补，不属于毁约范畴。</div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;border:0px;padding:0px;">关于预订：</div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;border:0px;padding:0px;">1、&nbsp;&nbsp;月租预订交<span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:'Times New Roman';">500</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:宋体;">刀</span>定金，可预订房间。口头预订不作保留，先到先得。在预约日期前两周取消预订，可退定金。少于两周取消不退定金。可提供国内银行账户接收定金（可按即时汇率支付人民币），入住后定金可转押金。</div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;border:0px;padding:0px;">2、 预约试住、短住预定的情况，可按预定天数的房租交定金，在预约日期前两周取消预订，可退定金，少于两周取消不退定金。</div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;border:0px;padding:0px;">关于交通：</div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;border:0px;padding:0px;">1、 机场接送，<span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:'Times New Roman';">50</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:宋体;">刀</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:'Times New Roman';">/</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:宋体;">趟。国际航班落地后第一时间联络我们，确认航班到达（国际线路时间时常有变化，有时早到，有时晚到，请在飞机落地后在机舱里就抓紧拨打电话，进入海关大楼以后电话没有信号，一般从飞机落地到过海关，取行李要一个小时左右刚好是我们接到电话赶到机场的时间）美国境内转机请在起飞前跟我们确认时间，由于国内一些手机在米国不能用</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:'Times New Roman';">(</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:宋体;">国产品牌一般不支持三频</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:'Times New Roman';">)</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:宋体;">，建议携带一个淘汰的</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:'Times New Roman';">Nokia</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:宋体;">手机备用，以免联系不上</span>。</div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;border:0px;padding:0px;">2、 如选择在PIH<span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:宋体;">大楼产检，惠提尔和长老教会医院</span>生产，每周一次例行产检免费接送（不包括孕妇家属，孕妇优先，有空位的情况下家属可用车，租车或购车的家庭不退免费赠送的交通费），生产入院、出院各免费接送一次、满月复诊免费接送一次。如果选在其他的地方产检及生产，酌情收取一定接送费用，如蒙市，圣市，<span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:'Times New Roman';">LA downtown</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:宋体;">单程</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:'Times New Roman';">20</span>刀。之外的体检或检验抽血、保胎、剖腹产拆线，生产家属接送，看儿科医生等等交通收费按1<span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:宋体;">英里</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:'Times New Roman';">1</span>刀计算。</div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;border:0px;padding:0px;">3、 远程购物、包车。沙漠<span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:'Times New Roman';">outlet</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:宋体;">、洛杉矶一日游等，</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:'Times New Roman';">250</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:宋体;">刀</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:'Times New Roman';">/</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:宋体;">天</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:'Times New Roman';">/</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:宋体;">车。可</span>多人分摊。其他接送根据距离酌情收费。</div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;border:0px;padding:0px;">4、 买菜都是跟我们出去，一般去香港，大华，<span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:'Times New Roman';">costco</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:宋体;">。 我们如果去逛街也可以跟出去，不额外收费。</span></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;border:0px;padding:0px;">5、 月租车，650<span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:宋体;">刀</span>/月，租期至少一个月。长租优惠。短租每天40<span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:宋体;">刀</span>/天。押金<span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:'Times New Roman';">650</span><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:宋体;">刀。</span></div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;border:0px;padding:0px;">6、&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:宋体;">住宿期间因为客人原因产生的交通罚款需要客人照章付费，例如：拒绝绑安全带，拒绝使用婴儿座椅，乱停车等被开的罚单。严重者会直接影响车辆保险额度。请自觉遵守交规，入乡随俗，美国不可能开后门找关系，除了交罚款就是上庭讲理，言行礼貌守规矩</span>。</div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;border:0px;padding:0px;">关于设施：</div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;border:0px;padding:0px;">1、 提供家具，床上用品，水电气，以及所有电器（包括冰箱、空调、烤箱、微波炉、洗衣机、干衣机、电视等）；</div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;border:0px;padding:0px;">2、 全屋无限高速上网，点播电影、三十几个中文电视频道，不限时拨打和接听米国、天朝、香港电话。</div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;border:0px;padding:0px;">3、 月子餐食谱指导，月子护理指导，海量育儿资料、育儿经验、音乐分享。</div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;border:0px;padding:0px;">附加服务：</div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;border:0px;padding:0px;">1、 暂时不提供待产期间伙食。如果非常有需要，需提供包餐以及照看初生妈妈和小宝贝的服务。酌情收费。</div>
<div align="left" style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;border:0px;padding:0px;">2、 提供孩子上学、入托及参加夏令营等活动的咨询帮助。</div>
