<p style="word-wrap:break-word;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;"><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#494949;"><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;background-color:#c9f3e9;"><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:simsun;"><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;">补充说明：</span></span></span></span></p>
<p style="word-wrap:break-word;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;"><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#494949;"><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;background-color:#c9f3e9;"><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:simsun;"><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;">很多人询问包餐的事，我在此说一下，以免老是重复回答。</span></span></span></span></p>
<p style="word-wrap:break-word;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;"><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#494949;"><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;background-color:#c9f3e9;"><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:simsun;"><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;">我家不做包餐，基于以下几个原因：</span></span></span></span></p>
<p style="word-wrap:break-word;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;"><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#494949;"><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;background-color:#c9f3e9;"><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:simsun;"><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;">1，天南海北的口味，专业厨师也满足不了每个妈妈的要求。平时大家怎么吃，自己做的，怎么都好。但如果我收了钱，算是服务，明知做不到让人满意，我还去赚这个钱，这不是我做人的风格。外面的饭店，你还有很多选择，包餐名宿，有啥吃啥，这滋味，自己想去了。</span></span></span></span></p>
<p style="word-wrap:break-word;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;"><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#494949;"><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;background-color:#c9f3e9;"><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:simsun;"><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;">2，如果你真什么都不会做，建议你天天吃饭店。我家附近的几个中餐、日餐，价格都很实惠，吃顿饭也就几刀的事情。不光是这里，吃遍美国，价格也是很便宜的。每天两顿吃饭店，一天下来也不会超过20刀，质量比包餐名宿，根本不是一个水平。米帝的饮食，从生到熟都不贵，9刀的自助餐，在国内至少得100RMB的水平。名宿包餐，每月最少我见过收800的，1000多得，也不在少数。租一辆车，天天跑出去吃自助，也不过这个钱。什么最划算，自己算吧。</span></span></span></span></p>
<p style="word-wrap:break-word;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;"><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#494949;"><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;background-color:#c9f3e9;"><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;font-family:simsun;"><span style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;">3，接触的人太多了，目前为止还没遇到一个妈妈对包餐名宿给好评的，基本上最终都是不欢而散，或者忍气吞声，到生完孩子，归心似箭的逃离米国，没有留下一丝对米帝的好印象，以为米帝也就是这样。可悲可叹。相对的，自己解决伙食，安排日常生活购物，切身体会米帝普通人的生活的众多妈妈，大都对米帝依依不舍。</span></span></span></span></p>";s:5:"finer";s:1:"0";s:5:"level";s:1:"0";s:5:"video";s:0:"";}s:8:"dosubmit";s:3:"yes";}
