<?PHP exit;?>	2013-09-14 13:08:48	admin	121.230.203.161	item:subject_edit	a:4:{s:6:"module";s:4:"item";s:3:"act";s:12:"subject_edit";s:4:"page";i:1;s:6:"offset";i:20;}	a:5:{s:7:"forward";s:65:"http://www.freebabydiy.com/admin.php?module=item&act=subject_list";s:3:"pid";s:2:"10";s:6:"t_item";a:22:{s:6:"status";s:1:"1";s:5:"thumb";s:51:"uploads/pictures/2013-09-14/thumb_45_1379134105.jpg";s:10:"templateid";s:1:"0";s:5:"catid";s:1:"0";s:4:"name";s:18:"天涯之家民宿";s:7:"subname";s:0:"";s:3:"aid";s:2:"93";s:11:"description";s:0:"";s:8:"mappoint";s:0:"";s:17:"c_citizen_contact";s:6:"天涯";s:13:"c_citizen_tel";s:12:"469 579 7357";s:12:"c_citizen_qq";s:8:"99626967";s:15:"c_citizen_email";s:0:"";s:16:"c_citizen_price1";s:3:"900";s:16:"c_citizen_price2";s:1:"0";s:14:"c_citizen_rent";s:1:"0";s:14:"c_citizen_food";s:1:"2";s:17:"c_citizen_booking";s:1:"1";s:7:"content";s:23876:"<span style="color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;">1，民宿简介：</span><br style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;" />
<br style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;" />
<span style="color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;">a,天涯之家位于加利福尼亚州的洛杉矶，全美最宜居城市walnut，传说中的核桃市，绿树成荫，学位社区，其核桃高中全美排名前五。是个绝对安全、超级安静的社区。不夸张地说，可以夜不闭户。天涯之家到幼儿园、小学、公园(可见到野生的鸳鸯、白鹭）步行2分钟；5分钟步行即可到VONS超市；10分钟到豆腐坊；开车5分钟到图书馆。该栋house室内使用面积2300尺（不含车库），约200平方米。屋前屋后左右均有宽阔花园草坪。楼上一个大客厅，楼下小客厅、餐厅，有充裕的公共活动空间。</span><br style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;" />
<br />
<span style="color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;">共5个房间。可出租4个房间，全部为雅房，不带独立卫生间，两个房间一个卫生间(需要独立卫生间的爸妈请勿联系)。根据不同的面积和配置，试运营期间，1号添喜(楼下小房)房租850刀，2号添乐(楼下大房)950刀、3号添平（楼上小房）900刀，4号添安（楼上大房）950刀，此为预订3个月以上的的价格，不足三个月者，退房收300手续费。不足月的部分，按照30天的百分比计算，决不搞最低算半个月之类的计算方式。如成本变化不大，将保持此价格。</span><br style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;" />
<br style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;" />
<span style="color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;">关于价格，不在乎环境，需要更低廉价格的，请移步蒙特利公园、罗兰岗、哈先达岗等地。议价勿扰。</span><br style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;" />
<br style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;" />
<span style="color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;">本宅绝对不是低价，但低价的绝对没我这环境，能够得上我这环境的，价格绝对比这高。敢把所有信息放在这，欢迎对比。</span><br style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;" />
<br style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;" />
<span style="color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;">b,陪客收费：陪客不分大小，每人每天收10刀，每月最多收25天；</span><br style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;" />
<br style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;" />
<span style="color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;">c,月子收费：月子自助做饭，按增加一个陪客计算。</span><br style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;" />
<br style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;" />
<span style="color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;">2,天涯一家：</span><br style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;" />
<br style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;" />
<span style="color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;天涯，厚道讲原则。有1个贤惠善良的老婆，由上班一族沦为家庭主妇，疯狂爱上了做面食。2个非常可爱的女儿，苗苗3岁半在天朝上幼儿园，喜欢跳舞；丫丫7个月，人称白富美小姐，体验美国式育儿方式。</span><br style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;" />
<br style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;" />
<span style="color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;">3，房间预订：</span><br style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;" />
<br style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;" />
<span style="color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;预订交500刀押金，可保留房间。口头预订不作保留，先到先得。在预约日期前一个月取消预订，可退定金，退订收10刀人工费。少于一个月取消不退款。</span><br style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;" />
<br style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;" />
<span style="color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;">4，房租缴纳：</span><br style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;" />
<br style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;" />
<span style="color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;">a,按月付月租，需缴纳押金500刀，提前两周通知离开，押金可退，未提前通知离开，押金不退。</span><br style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;" />
<br style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;" />
<span style="color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;">b,入住时一次性缴纳3个月房租，免押金。超过3个月续交。</span><br style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;" />
<br style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;" />
<span style="color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;">c,入住时间不满一个月离开，按家庭旅馆收费，每日60刀。</span><br style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;" />
<br style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;" />
<span style="color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;">d,预约试住，可以随时离开，按家庭旅馆收费，每日60刀。从决定长住开始，转长住另算。</span><br style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;" />
<br style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;" />
<span style="color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;">5，免费项目：</span><br style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;" />
