<br style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;" />
<span style="color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;生产日期无法预测，早产或晚产结账时多退少补，不属于毁约范畴。</span><br style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;" />
<br style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;" />
