<span style="color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;">天涯极力为妈妈们营造家庭氛围，时常组织集体活动，希望所有妈妈生活愉快。寻找志趣相投的爸妈入住。</span><br style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;" />
<br style="word-wrap:break-word;margin:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;" />
